import React from 'react'
import {Link} from 'react-router-dom'
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar'
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav'

function HeaderComponent() {
    const isUserLoggedIn = false
    return (        
        <header>
            <Navbar variant="dark" >
                <Navbar.Brand href="/home">Birthday Calendar</Navbar.Brand>
                <Nav className="navbar-collapse justify-content-end">
                    {!isUserLoggedIn && <Nav.Link href='/login'>Log In</Nav.Link>}
                    {!isUserLoggedIn && <Nav.Link href='/signup'>Get Started</Nav.Link>}
                    {isUserLoggedIn && <Nav.Link href='/logout'>Log Out</Nav.Link>}                    
                </Nav>
            </Navbar>
        </header>
    )
}

export default HeaderComponent
